<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-color-mode="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>RadSOC ¬∑ Security Operations Platform for Physical Security Devices</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Unified security operations center for physical security devices. Monitor, manage, and respond to threats across your entire security infrastructure.">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --color-canvas-default: #0d1117;
            --color-canvas-subtle: #161b22;
            --color-border-default: #30363d;
            --color-border-muted: #21262d;
            --color-fg-default: #e6edf3;
            --color-fg-muted: #7d8590;
            --color-fg-subtle: #6e7681;
            --color-accent-fg: #2f81f7;
            --color-accent-emphasis: #1f6feb;
            --color-success-fg: #3fb950;
            --color-success-emphasis: #238636;
            --color-danger-fg: #f85149;
            --color-done-fg: #a371f7;
            --color-sponsors-fg: #db61a2;
            --color-neutral-emphasis-plus: #6e7681;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI","Noto Sans",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif,"Apple Color Emoji","Segoe UI Emoji";
            background: var(--color-canvas-default);
            color: var(--color-fg-default);
            line-height: 1.5;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            background: rgba(13, 17, 23, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
        }

        .header-container {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--color-fg-default);
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 24px;
            list-style: none;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--color-fg-default);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--color-fg-muted);
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn-header {
            padding: 5px 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            background: var(--color-fg-default);
            color: var(--color-canvas-default);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-header:hover {
            background: var(--color-fg-muted);
        }

        /* Vertical Tabs Section */
        .vertical-tabs-section {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 80px 32px;
        }

        .vertical-tabs-intro {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 80px;
        }

        .vertical-tabs-wrapper {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
            gap: 80px;
            align-items: start;
        }

        .vertical-tabs-nav {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 4px;
        }

        .vertical-tab-button {
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border: none;
            background: none;
            color: var(--color-fg-muted);
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: left;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            border-left: 3px solid transparent;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        .vertical-tab-button:hover {
            color: var(--color-fg-default);
            background: rgba(110, 118, 129, 0.1);
        }

        .vertical-tab-button.active {
            color: var(--color-fg-default);
            border-left-color: var(--color-success-emphasis);
            background: rgba(35, 134, 54, 0.1);
        }

        .vertical-tabs-content {
            min-height: 600px;
        }

        .vertical-tab-panel {
            display: none;
        }

        .vertical-tab-panel.active {
            display: block;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.4s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .river-item {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 64px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .river-item.reverse {
            direction: rtl;
        }

        .river-item.reverse > * {
            direction: ltr;
        }

        .river-content h3 {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--color-success-fg);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .river-content h2 {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .river-content p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--color-fg-muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .river-visual {
            background: var(--color-canvas-subtle);
            border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 48px;
            min-height: 400px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--color-fg-muted);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .river-visual:hover {
            border-color: var(--color-border-muted);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        /* Hero */
        .hero {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 128px 32px 80px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 800px;
            height: 400px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(35, 134, 54, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 80px;
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -0.04em;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #e6edf3 0%, #7d8590 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .hero-description {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: var(--color-fg-muted);
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--color-success-emphasis);
            color: var(--color-fg-default);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(35, 134, 54, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: var(--color-success-fg);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(35, 134, 54, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            border: 1px solid var(--color-neutral-emphasis-plus);
            color: var(--color-fg-default);
            background: transparent;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            border-color: var(--color-fg-muted);
            background: rgba(110, 118, 129, 0.1);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        /* Stats Bar */
        .stats-bar {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 48px 32px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 80px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .stat {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-value {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--color-fg-default);
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--color-fg-muted);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }

        /* Features */
        .features {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 80px 32px;
        }

        .section-intro {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 64px;
        }

        .section-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--color-success-fg);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .section-heading {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .section-description {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: var(--color-fg-muted);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .features-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0;
        }

        .feature-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr;
            gap: 24px;
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .feature-row:hover {
            transform: translateX(4px);
        }

        .feature-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .feature-icon-simple {
            font-size: 32px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            justify-content: center;
            padding-top: 4px;
        }

        .feature-content-simple h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: var(--color-fg-default);
        }

        .feature-content-simple p {
            color: var(--color-fg-muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .feature-list {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .feature-list li {
            color: var(--color-fg-muted);
            padding: 6px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            position: relative;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .feature-list li::before {
            content: '‚úì';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--color-success-fg);
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Breakout Section */
        .breakout {
            background: var(--color-canvas-subtle);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
            padding: 80px 32px;
            margin: 80px 0;
        }

        .breakout-container {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 64px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .breakout-content h2 {
            font-size: 40px;
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .breakout-content p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--color-fg-muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .breakout-image {
            background: var(--color-canvas-default);
            border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 32px;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--color-fg-muted);
            min-height: 300px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        /* CTA */
        .cta {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 120px 32px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .cta h2 {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .cta p {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: var(--color-fg-muted);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
            padding: 40px 32px;
            background: var(--color-canvas-subtle);
        }

        .footer-container {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .footer-brand {
            color: var(--color-fg-muted);
        }

        .footer-brand .logo {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: var(--color-fg-default);
        }

        .footer-column h4 {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: var(--color-fg-default);
        }

        .footer-links {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .footer-links li {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            color: var(--color-accent-fg);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer-links a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
            color: var(--color-success-fg);
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 32px;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--color-fg-subtle);
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 56px;
            }

            .breakout-container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .footer-container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-links {
                display: none;
            }

            .hero {
                padding: 80px 24px 48px;
            }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 40px;
            }

            .hero-description {
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            .section-heading {
                font-size: 32px;
            }

            .breakout-content h2 {
                font-size: 32px;
            }

            .cta h2 {
                font-size: 32px;
            }

            .footer-container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 32px;
            }

            .feature-row {
                grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr;
                gap: 16px;
                padding: 32px 0;
            }

            .feature-icon-simple {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .feature-content-simple h3 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .feature-content-simple p {
                font-size: 15px;
            }

            .vertical-tabs-wrapper {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 32px;
            }

            .vertical-tabs-nav {
                flex-direction: row;
                overflow-x: auto;
                -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
            }

            .vertical-tab-button {
                white-space: nowrap;
            }

            .river-item {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 32px;
            }

            .river-item.reverse {
                direction: ltr;
            }

            .river-content h2 {
                font-size: 32px;
            }

            .river-visual {
                min-height: 300px;
                padding: 32px;
            }

            .stats-bar {
                gap: 40px;
                padding: 32px 24px;
            }

            .stat-value {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <div class="header-container">
            <div class="logo">RadSOC</div>
            <nav>
                <ul class="nav-links">
                    <li><a href="#platform">Platform</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#devices">Devices</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#pricing">Pricing</a></li>
                    <li><button class="btn-header">Get Started</button></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <h1>The security operations<br>platform that scales</h1>
            <p class="hero-description">RadSOC unifies your physical security infrastructure into a single command center. Monitor, detect, and respond to threats across cameras, access control, and sensors‚Äîfrom one intelligent platform.</p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
                <a href="#get-started" class="btn btn-primary">Start free trial</a>
                <a href="#demo" class="btn btn-secondary">Schedule demo</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="stats-bar">
            <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-value">100K+</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Devices monitored</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-value">99.9%</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Uptime SLA</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-value">&lt;10ms</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Alert latency</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-value">24/7</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Support included</span>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="vertical-tabs-section">
            <div class="vertical-tabs-intro">
                <div class="section-label">How it works</div>
                <h2 class="section-heading">Security operations that just work</h2>
                <p class="section-description">Four core capabilities that transform how you protect your infrastructure</p>
            </div>

            <div class="vertical-tabs-wrapper">
                <nav class="vertical-tabs-nav">
                    <button class="vertical-tab-button active" data-tab="monitor">Monitor</button>
                    <button class="vertical-tab-button" data-tab="detect">Detect</button>
                    <button class="vertical-tab-button" data-tab="respond">Respond</button>
                    <button class="vertical-tab-button" data-tab="analyze">Analyze</button>
                </nav>

                <div class="vertical-tabs-content">
                    <div class="vertical-tab-panel active" id="monitor">
                        <div class="river-item">
                            <div class="river-content">
                                <h3>Monitor</h3>
                                <h2>See everything, miss nothing</h2>
                                <p>Real-time visibility across your entire security infrastructure. Track device health, network status, and performance metrics in a unified dashboard that updates every second.</p>
                                <ul class="feature-list" style="margin-left: 0;">
                                    <li>Live status for 1000+ devices simultaneously</li>
                                    <li>Automated health checks with predictive maintenance</li>
                                    <li>Network topology mapping and connectivity tracking</li>
                                    <li>Custom performance thresholds and instant alerts</li>
                                </ul>
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 24px;">Watch live demo ‚Üí</a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="river-visual">
                                <p style="font-size: 18px;">Real-time Monitoring Dashboard</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="vertical-tab-panel" id="detect">
                        <div class="river-item reverse">
                            <div class="river-content">
                                <h3>Detect</h3>
                                <h2>Threats detected before they escalate</h2>
                                <p>AI-powered detection that learns your environment. Reduce false positives by 95% while catching real threats faster with behavioral analysis and smart correlation.</p>
                                <ul class="feature-list" style="margin-left: 0;">
                                    <li>Machine learning models trained on your baseline</li>
                                    <li>Behavioral pattern recognition across device types</li>
                                    <li>Multi-sensor correlation for verified incidents</li>
                                    <li>Automatic threat classification and severity scoring</li>
                                </ul>
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 24px;">See how AI works ‚Üí</a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="river-visual">
                                <p style="font-size: 18px;">Threat Detection Engine</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="vertical-tab-panel" id="respond">
                        <div class="river-item">
                            <div class="river-content">
                                <h3>Respond</h3>
                                <h2>Response time: milliseconds</h2>
                                <p>Automated playbooks that react faster than any human team. Lock doors, trigger alarms, and notify personnel instantly when threats are detected‚Äîno manual intervention required.</p>
                                <ul class="feature-list" style="margin-left: 0;">
                                    <li>50+ pre-configured response playbooks ready to deploy</li>
                                    <li>Visual workflow builder for custom automation chains</li>
                                    <li>Multi-device orchestration across your infrastructure</li>
                                    <li>Smart escalation with on-call scheduling integration</li>
                                </ul>
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 24px;">Build your playbook ‚Üí</a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="river-visual">
                                <p style="font-size: 18px;">Automated Response Workflows</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="vertical-tab-panel" id="analyze">
                        <div class="river-item reverse">
                            <div class="river-content">
                                <h3>Analyze</h3>
                                <h2>Data that drives decisions</h2>
                                <p>Turn security data into strategic insights. Identify patterns, optimize resource allocation, and prove compliance with comprehensive analytics and one-click reports.</p>
                                <ul class="feature-list" style="margin-left: 0;">
                                    <li>Drag-and-drop dashboard builder with 100+ widgets</li>
                                    <li>Historical analysis with unlimited data retention</li>
                                    <li>SOC 2, HIPAA, and PCI compliance report templates</li>
                                    <li>Scheduled exports to PDF, Excel, or direct to stakeholders</li>
                                </ul>
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 24px;">Explore dashboards ‚Üí</a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="river-visual">
                                <p style="font-size: 18px;">Analytics & Reporting</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="features" class="features">
            <div class="section-intro">
                <div class="section-label">Platform</div>
                <h2 class="section-heading">Built for security teams that need results</h2>
                <p class="section-description">Everything you need to monitor, detect, and respond to threats across your physical security infrastructure</p>
            </div>

            <div class="features-list">
                <div class="feature-row">
                    <div class="feature-icon-simple">üìπ</div>
                    <div class="feature-content-simple">
                        <h3>Unified Device Management</h3>
                        <p>Stop switching between vendor dashboards. Control cameras, access systems, and sensors from one interface. Get instant status updates, push firmware remotely, and manage 1000+ devices as easily as 10.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-row">
                    <div class="feature-icon-simple">üîî</div>
                    <div class="feature-content-simple">
                        <h3>Intelligent Alerting</h3>
                        <p>Cut alert noise by 95%. AI-powered correlation connects related events across devices so you see incidents, not individual alerts. Customizable rules adapt to your environment and send notifications where your team already works.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-row">
                    <div class="feature-icon-simple">üìä</div>
                    <div class="feature-content-simple">
                        <h3>Real-Time Analytics</h3>
                        <p>Transform raw security data into strategic insights. Build custom dashboards in minutes, analyze historical patterns to prevent future incidents, and generate compliance reports for auditors in one click.</p>
                    </div>
